data.description: 1458 Oakwood Ave, Louisville, KY 40215, is a charming brick home boasting modern amenities and recent upgrades. With a spacious 1,194 square feet of living space, this residence offers a comfortable living experience. The property features renovated kitchen, bathroom, and flooring, providing a contemporary touch to the interior. The roof, furnace, air conditioning, and water heater, all installed in 2020 or 2021, ensure efficiency and reliability. Additionally, the four-car garage adds convenience and ample parking space to this attractive home. Don't let this one get away. Come schedule your private showing today before its gone.
